item.title: STA 215
item.description: Nothing in this syllabus will be set in stone or taken for granted. This is not designed to be a map, but rather a starting place with the goal of vigorously rewiting the syllabus as we go, discovering what we will learn together as we learn it, and questioning what we will do even as we being. Drop-in Hours I will be holding virtual drop-in hours throughout the Fall 2021.
